{"page_id": 55531, "slug": "Evangelion_Unit-02_(Other)", "title": "Evangelion Unit-02 (Other)", "display_title": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Evangelion Unit-02 (Other)</span>", "namespace": 0, "content_model": "wikitext", "language": null, "wikitext": "<span style=\"font-size:200%\"><code>[[Evangelion Unit-02|NGE]]</code> <code>[[Evangelion Unit-02 (NTE)|NTE]]</code> <code>[[Evangelion Unit-02 (Anima)|Anima]]</code> <code>'''Other'''</code></span>\n\n===Girlfriend of Steel===\nIn [[Girlfriend of Steel]], Unit-02 is the first to make contact with the downed [[Extracanonical_Mecha#Robots|T-RIDEN-T]]\n\n===Pachinko===\nIn pachinko/pachislot machines, NGE Unit-02 is often seen wielding the dual chainsaw from the manga\n\n===Transformers mode EVA===\nUnit-02 is notably absent in the collab; after Unit-01 was damaged, Misato states that Nerv has no Evas left that can be sortied.", "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><span style=\"font-size:200%\"><code><a href=\"/Evangelion_Unit-02\" title=\"Evangelion Unit-02\">NGE</a></code> <code><a href=\"/Evangelion_Unit-02_(NTE)\" title=\"Evangelion Unit-02 (NTE)\">NTE</a></code> <code><a href=\"/Evangelion_Unit-02_(Anima)\" title=\"Evangelion Unit-02 (Anima)\">Anima</a></code> <code><b>Other</b></code></span>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Girlfriend_of_Steel\">Girlfriend of Steel</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Evangelion_Unit-02_(Other)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Girlfriend of Steel\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/Girlfriend_of_Steel\" title=\"Girlfriend of Steel\">Girlfriend of Steel</a>, Unit-02 is the first to make contact with the downed <a href=\"/Extracanonical_Mecha#Robots\" title=\"Extracanonical Mecha\">T-RIDEN-T</a>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Pachinko\">Pachinko</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Evangelion_Unit-02_(Other)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Pachinko\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>In pachinko/pachislot machines, NGE Unit-02 is often seen wielding the dual chainsaw from the manga\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Transformers_mode_EVA\">Transformers mode EVA</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Evangelion_Unit-02_(Other)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Transformers mode EVA\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Unit-02 is notably absent in the collab; after Unit-01 was damaged, Misato states that Nerv has no Evas left that can be sortied.\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260417025739\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.002 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.002 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 15/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key mediawikidb-ew_:pcache:idhash:55531-0!canonical and timestamp 20260417025739 and revision id 113442. Rendering was triggered because: page-view\n -->\n</div>", "summary": "NGE NTE Anima Other", "sections": [{"toclevel": 1, "level": "3", "line": "Girlfriend of Steel", "number": "1", "index": "1", "fromtitle": "Evangelion_Unit-02_(Other)", "byteoffset": 198, "anchor": "Girlfriend_of_Steel", "linkAnchor": "Girlfriend_of_Steel"}, {"toclevel": 1, "level": "3", "line": "Pachinko", "number": "2", "index": "2", "fromtitle": "Evangelion_Unit-02_(Other)", "byteoffset